byline.original: By SHEILA M. ELDRED and JOHN ELIGON

headline.print_headline: Doctor Saw Prince a Day Before His Death
headline.main: Prince’s Doctor Arrived With Test Results Only to Find Him Dead

snippet: Dr. Michael T. Schulenberg had seen Prince the previous day, according to a police affidavit filed in connection with a search warrant for his medical records.
abstract: Affidavit filed by sheriff's office in Carver County, Minn, says Dr Michael T Schulenberg, who had treated Prince twice in recent weeks, turned up at musician's estate on morning he died to give him results of medical tests; warrant seeks medical records from North Memorial Medical Center, part of health care network within which Schulenberg practiced.
